NAME
    Sub::Spec::Wrapper - Wrap subroutines

VERSION
    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
     use Sub::Spec::Wrapper;

DESCRIPTION
    WARNING: PRELIMINARY VERSION, NOT EVERYTHING DESCRIBED IS IMPLEMENTED

    This module provides wrap() that implements/utilizes many spec clauses,
    like "args", "result", "timeout", etc.

    This module uses Log::Any for logging.

FUNCTIONS
    None are exported, but they are exportable.

SEE ALSO
    Sub::Spec

AUTHOR
